Horde AI Companion Kick
    Events
        Unit - A unit Starts the effect of an ability
    Conditions
        (Ability being cast) Equal to Kick Companion 
        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
            Conditions
                ((Target unit of ability being cast) is in Companion_Group.) Equal to True
                ((Target unit of ability being cast) is in TamedUnits.) Equal to True
    Actions
        Trigger - Turn off (This trigger)
        Set VariableSet CompanionUnitKicked = (Target unit of ability being cast)
        Sound - Play UpkeepRing <gen>
        Set VariableSet PartyKickVoice = (Random integer number between 1 and 3)
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                PartyKickVoice Equal to 1
            Then - Actions
                Cinematic - Send transmission to (All players) from Nazgrek named Nazgrek: Play Nazgrek_0002 <gen> and display Farewell for now, u....  Modify duration: Set to 3.00 seconds and Don't wait
            Else - Actions
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        PartyKickVoice Equal to 2
                    Then - Actions
                        Cinematic - Send transmission to (All players) from Nazgrek named Nazgrek: Play Nazgrek_0003 <gen> and display It’s been a pleas....  Modify duration: Set to 3.00 seconds and Don't wait
                    Else - Actions
                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                            If - Conditions
                                PartyKickVoice Equal to 3
                            Then - Actions
                                Cinematic - Send transmission to (All players) from Nazgrek named Nazgrek: Play Nazgrek_0004 <gen> and display Until our paths cro....  Modify duration: Set to 3.00 seconds and Don't wait
                            Else - Actions
        Wait 3.50 seconds
        -------- ========= Hero companions --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                CompanionUnitKicked Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Rogue
            Then - Actions
                Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Proper name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  has been kicked from the party!)
                Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Player 6 (Orange) and Retain color
                Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Kicked Rogue <gen> (checking conditions)
            Else - Actions
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        CompanionUnitKicked Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Warlock
                    Then - Actions
                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Proper name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  has been kicked from the party!)
                        Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Player 6 (Orange) and Retain color
                        Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Kicked Warlock <gen> (checking conditions)
                    Else - Actions
                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                            If - Conditions
                                CompanionUnitKicked Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Shaman
                            Then - Actions
                                Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Proper name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  has been kicked from the party!)
                                Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Player 6 (Orange) and Retain color
                                Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Kicked Restoshaman <gen> (checking conditions)
                            Else - Actions
                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                    If - Conditions
                                        CompanionUnitKicked Equal to NPC_Horde_AI_Warrior
                                    Then - Actions
                                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Proper name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  has been kicked from the party!)
                                        Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Player 6 (Orange) and Retain color
                                        Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Kicked Warrior <gen> (checking conditions)
                                    Else - Actions
                                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                            If - Conditions
                                                CompanionUnitKicked Equal to NPC_Neutral_Engineer
                                            Then - Actions
                                                Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Proper name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  has been kicked from the party!)
                                                Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Player 7 (Green) and Retain color
                                                Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Kicked Engineer <gen> (checking conditions)
                                            Else - Actions
                                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                                    If - Conditions
                                                        CompanionUnitKicked Equal to NPC_Riverbane_Paladin
                                                    Then - Actions
                                                        Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Proper name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  has been kicked from the party!)
                                                        Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Player 15 (Turquoise) and Retain color
                                                        Trigger - Run Horde NPC Chat Kicked Paladin <gen> (checking conditions)
                                                    Else - Actions
        -------- ========= Remove Companion from the group --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (CompanionUnitKicked is in Companion_Group.) Equal to True
                (CompanionUnitKicked is A Hero) Equal to True
            Then - Actions
                Unit - Order CompanionUnitKicked to Stop.
                Game - Display to (All players) the text: (Debug Kick:  + (Kicked from Companion_Group:  + (Proper name of CompanionUnitKicked)))
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from Companion_Group.
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from CompanionFocusNazgrek.
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from CompanionFocusZulkis.
                Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Remove Companion <gen> (checking conditions)
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        (Level of Wander (Neutral) for CompanionUnitKicked) Greater than 0
                    Then - Actions
                        Unit - Remove Wander (Neutral) from CompanionUnitKicked
                    Else - Actions
            Else - Actions
        -------- ========= Tamed unit --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (CompanionUnitKicked is in TamedUnits.) Equal to True
            Then - Actions
                Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  is no longer your beast and will not following you!)
                -------- Disable XP for the unit --------
                Custom script:   call UnitExperience_DisableXP(udg_TamedUnit, true)
                -------- - --------
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from TamedUnits.
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from CompanionFocusNazgrek.
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from CompanionFocusZulkis.
                Unit - Order CompanionUnitKicked to Stop.
                Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Neutral Passive and Retain color
                Unit - Add Wander (Neutral) to CompanionUnitKicked
                Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Remove Tamed <gen> (checking conditions)
                Custom script:   call UnitExperience_DisableXP(udg_TamedUnit, true)
                Set VariableSet TamedUnit = No unit
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        CompanionUnitKicked Equal to Shadowclaw
                    Then - Actions
                        -------- IF SHADOWCLAW --------
                        Unit - Make Shadowclaw Invulnerable
                        Unit - Change ownership of CompanionUnitKicked to Player 19 (Mint) and Retain color
                        Set VariableSet VarPoint = (Center of NazgrekIntroPoint <gen>)
                        Unit - Order Shadowclaw to Move To VarPoint
                        Custom script:   call RemoveLocation(udg_VarPoint)
                    Else - Actions
            Else - Actions
        -------- ========= Regular unit --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (CompanionUnitKicked is in Companion_Group.) Equal to True
                (CompanionUnitKicked is A Hero) Not equal to True
            Then - Actions
                Unit - Order CompanionUnitKicked to Stop.
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from Companion_Group.
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from CompanionFocusNazgrek.
                Unit Group - Remove CompanionUnitKicked from CompanionFocusZulkis.
                Game - Display to (All players) the text: ((Name of CompanionUnitKicked) +  has been kicked from the party!)
                Set VariableSet CompVarPoint = (Random point in (Playable map area))
                Unit - Order CompanionUnitKicked to Attack-Move To CompVarPoint
                Unit - Add a 60.00 second Generic expiration timer to CompanionUnitKicked
                Custom script:   call RemoveLocation(udg_CompVarPoint)
                Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Remove Companion <gen> (checking conditions)
            Else - Actions
        -------- ========= ===================== --------
        -------- ========= TURN ON trigger --------
        Wait 1.50 seconds
        Trigger - Turn on (This trigger)
